T1  - On Multi-Agent Cognitive Cooperation: Can virtual agents behave like humans?
AU  - D’Avella, Salvatore
AU  - Camacho-Gonzalez, Gerardo
AU  - Tripicchio, Paolo
JO  - Neurocomputing
VL  - 480
SP  - 27
